Enum Constant Detail

THETA_JOIN

public static final NestedLoopsJoin.Type THETA_JOIN
A constant specifying a theta-join. Only the tuples for which the specified predicate is true will be returned.

LEFT_OUTER_JOIN

public static final NestedLoopsJoin.Type LEFT_OUTER_JOIN
A constant specifying a left outer-join. The tuples for which the specified predicate is true as well as all elements of input0 not qualifying concerning the predicate will be returned. The function newResult is called with an element of input0 and the null value.

RIGHT_OUTER_JOIN

public static final NestedLoopsJoin.Type RIGHT_OUTER_JOIN
A constant specifying a right outer-join. The tuples for which the specified predicate is true as well as all elements of input1 not qualifying concerning the predicate will be returned. The function newResult is called with an element of input1 and the null value.

OUTER_JOIN

public static final NestedLoopsJoin.Type OUTER_JOIN
A constant specifying a full outer-join. The tuples for which the specified predicate is true as well as all tuples additionally returned by the left and right outer-join will be returned.
